<br>
Group was 61 Mage, 61 warrior, 62 cleric, 65 Enchanter,<br>
               61 Rogue, 62 Rogue.<br>
<br>
The first try I got no crit nuke hits (have scf3) and a full resist on a nuke at the end of a mob on 4th wave. Failed.<br>
<br>
Second try I got about 5 crit nuke hits and no resists. Won easily.<br>
<br>
In my opinion it has a lot to do with how your nukes are landing as to how you are going to do.<br>
<br>
If you are having mana trouble, do not nuke the first mob engaged at the beginning of each wave, just assist with the pet. It will die in time as the Executioner doesn't spawn right away after the wave initially pops. Not having to nuke the first one of each wave should help any mana trouble you may have.<br>
<br>
I didn't use Banishment, though I did use exile summoned on the rocks.<br>
<br>
SOFB + SOS is ur best bet to use on the rest of the mobs imo.<br>
<br>
